bold; font-size:14.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >旅客运输管理</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（1）客运企业不得挂靠经营，不得违法转租、转让客运车辆和线路牌</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（2）客运企业所属的非营运性车辆严禁作为客运车辆从事经营</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（3）客运包车要凭包车客运标志牌，按照约定的时间、起始地、目的地和线路，持包车票</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"text-indent:26.2500pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >或包车合同运行，不得承运包车合同约定之外的旅客</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（4）客运企业与驾驶人要签订用工合同，发车前，提醒驾驶人要督促乘客系好安全带</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（5）客运企业应考虑自身是否有符合其经营范围和条件的相应运输能力</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（6）客运企业在调派运输业务时，应确认车辆，驾驶员是否符合安全生产工作要求</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >驾驶人培训</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >岗前培训</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-left:26.2500pt; text-indent:-26.2500pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（1）培训内容：国家道路交通安全和安全生产相关法律法规；安全行车知识；典型交通事故案例警示教育；职业道德；安全告知知识；应急处置知识；企业有关安全运营管理的规定。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（2）培训时间：理论培训不少于</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >12</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >学时；实际驾驶操作不少于</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >30</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >学时</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >日常培训</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（1）建立教育培训考核制度</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（2）培训内容：开展法律法规；典型交通事故案例警示；技能训练；应急处置等教育培训。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"text-indent:26.2500pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >组织和督促本企业的客运驾驶人参加继续教育，保证客运驾驶人参加教育和培训的时</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"text-indent:26.2500pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >间，提供必要的学习条件。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（3）培训时间：定期、每月不少于两次，每次不少于</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >小时</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >驾驶人考核</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >1</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >）建立考核制度</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >2</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >）考核内容：客运驾驶人违法驾驶情况；交通事故情况；服务质量；安全运营情况；安</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"text-indent:26.2500pt; margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >全操作规程执行情况；参加教育与培训情况以及客运驾驶人心理和生理健康状况等。</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " ><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=3Dp0  style=3D"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; " ><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >（</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >）考核周期：一般大于</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >3</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'; font-size:10.5000pt; font-family:'宋体'; " >个月</span><span style=3D"mso-spacerun:'yes'